metadata.name: ART BASEL TOUR 2022
metadata.description:
Featuring a new futuristic yet sentimental artistic style from DotConnector's first creative director & acclaimed digital artist Andre Oshea - collectors, the web3 curious and our community are invited to celebrate DotConnector's event series at Art Basel 2022 with this limited run, open edition "Tour Poster".
